@startuml
left to right direction

actor Cashier
node "Store Edge Terminal" {
  component "Self-Checkout UI\n(React)" as SC
  database "Local Queue\n(localStorage)" as LQ
}

cloud "Central Platform" {
  component "Backend API\n(FastAPI + SQLite)" as API
  component "Dashboard UI\n(React)" as DB
  database "Central SQLite" as CDB
}

Cashier --> SC : Scan / Add items
SC --> API : /auth/login (JWT)
SC --> API : /transactions (online)
SC --> LQ : Cache tx (offline)
SC --> API : /heartbeat
SC --> API : /sync/offline (batch)
API --> CDB : Idempotent writes
DB --> API : Dashboard APIs

@enduml
